673
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:20,020
Another time.

674
00:40:20,780 --> 00:40:21,500
Another time.

675
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:38,300
Mr. Sanmahu.

676
00:40:39,300 --> 00:40:40,100
Can't we

