687
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:03,140
It really has nothing to do with me!

688
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:04,100
Yeah, I know.

689
00:41:05,260 --> 00:41:06,140
None of this

690
00:41:06,420 --> 00:41:07,500
