such a big operation, Mr. Sanmahu.

696
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:18,660
Right?

697
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:19,820
Don't worry, Mr. Sanmahu.

698
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:20,820
When I get back,

699
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:22,420
I'll have a good talk with my boss.

700
00:41:22,420 --> 00:41:23,940
That Mr. Han!

701
00:41:26,220 --> 00:41:29,060
Do you think he's the kind of man
