733
00:44:18,540 --> 00:44:19,540
That's all?

734
00:44:20,420 --> 00:44:21,780
That's all.

735
00:44:24,340 --> 00:44:25,140
Sheng,

736
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:27,020
I'm giving you one more chance.

737
00:44:27,100 --> 00:44:29,020
Use your head.

738
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:30,980
Think carefully before you answer me.

739
00:44:35,260 --> 00:44:36,380
Mr. Zhan, I...

