759
00:45:28,740 --> 00:45:29,940
I'm working for you!

760
00:45:29,940 --> 00:45:31,860
Why would you tail me?

761
00:45:32,100 --> 00:45:33,540
You had your chance.

762
00:45:33,540 --> 00:45:34,780
Think it over,

763
00:45:35,220 --> 00:45:37,100
