807
00:48:08,500 --> 00:48:10,420
Basically, we help

808
00:48:10,420 --> 00:48:11,300
those big shots

809
00:48:11,420 --> 00:48:12,900
manage their accounts and stuff.

810
00:48:13,060 --> 00:48:13,700
That punk

811
00:48:14,060 --> 00:48:16,100
saw a recruitment post

812
00:48:16,860 --> 00:48:18,060
