813
00:48:18,180 --> 00:48:20,580
Get himself arrested for brawling,

814
00:48:20,580 --> 00:48:21,660
deliver a message to someone inside,

815
00:48:21,780 --> 00:48:23,900
then get bailed out under a settlement.

816
00:48:23,900 --> 00:48:25,660
