840
00:49:18,900 --> 00:49:21,060
What was it like the first time
you killed someone?

841
00:49:23,180 --> 00:49:24,380
Mr. Qian.

842
00:49:26,900 --> 00:49:27,900
What a shame.

843
00:49:35,100 --> 00:49:35,580
Mr. Tu.

844
00:49:37,980 --> 00:49:39,660
I'll kill you!

845
00:49:39,740 --> 00:49:40,340
Mr. Tu, calm down!

846
00:49:40,340 --> 00:49:41,300
Mr. Tu!

847
00:49:41,300 --> 00:49:42,220
Let go of me!

848
00:49:42,220 --> 00:49:42,580
Mr. Tu!

849
00:49:42,580 --> 00:49:43,780
