850
00:49:43,780 --> 00:49:44,340
Don't be rash, Mr. Tu!

851
00:49:44,740 --> 00:49:45,380
Quick!

852
00:49:45,380 --> 00:49:46,500
Get him out of here now!

853
00:49:47,300 --> 00:49:47,900
Don't be rash.

854
00:49:48,140 --> 00:49:49,020
Don't touch me!

855
00:49:51,780 --> 00:49:52,900
Mr. Qian was Mr. Tu's informant.

856
00:49:53,820 --> 00:49:54,980
