858
00:49:58,900 --> 00:49:59,780
Sheng,

859
00:50:00,300 --> 00:50:01,580
you're clever.

860
00:50:01,860 --> 00:50:03,420
But you've used your cleverness
in all the wrong ways.

861
00:50:03,900 --> 00:50:05,380
I'm giving you a chance now

862
00:50:05,380 --> 00:50:07,980
because you did some good things before.

863
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,740
I hope you understand what I'm saying.

864
00:50:10,940 --> 00:50:12,260
Think it over.

865
00:50:13,580 --> 00:50:15,220
This is your last chance.

866
